       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    PSI18202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA PSI18202.
      *
      *     Detalhe Ficheiro Aceite
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI18202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDDET002 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDHEADER END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA      END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV1820.
       COPY PSCV1821.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
      *     LINKAGE ARQUITECTURA
       COPY AQCL0001.
      *     TRATAMENTO DE ERROS
       COPY AQCW0009.
      *     LINKAGE DE API'S SX
       COPY SXCL0002.
      *     OBTEM NOME DO CLIENTE NA BANKA
       COPY SXCL0380.
      *     TRATAMENTO DE DEBUG
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY PSCK0001.
       COPY PSCK0002.
       COPY AQCW0005.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-PSDETALH               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSDETALH'.
           05 CON-PSHEADER               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSHEADER'.
           05 CON-PRG-NAME               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI18202'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSI18202'.
           05 WS-CNTA.
              10 WS-CNTA-NCLI            PIC 9(08) VALUE ZEROES.
              10 WS-CNTA-NATR            PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROES.
              10 WS-CNTA-NSEQ            PIC 9(01) VALUE ZEROES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI18202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV1820-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ASE               TO PSCV1821-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE PSCV1820-ADE       TO PSCV1821-ADE.

           PERFORM 2050-VALIDA-FICHEIRO
              THRU 2059-VALIDA-FICHEIRO-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND
              PSCV1821-ORCBAN EQUAL VIAL0001-CBANCO
      *
              PERFORM 2200-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF
                 THRU 2299-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2050-VALIDA-FICHEIRO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-VALIDA-FICHEIRO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-VALIDA-FICHEIRO'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNCLI '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORDINT '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORDINT        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNFIC '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNFIC        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNREG '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNREG        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNCLI            TO PSHEADER-HRNCLI.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORDINT            TO AQCW0005-DTX10.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98              TO PSHEADER-HRDINT.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNFIC            TO PSHEADER-HRNFIC.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT   HRSITU
                 INTO  :PSHEADER-HRSITU
                 FROM PSHEADER
                 WHERE HRNCLI  = :PSHEADER-HRNCLI
                   AND HRDINT  = :PSHEADER-HRDINT
                   AND HRNFIC  = :PSHEADER-HRNFIC
           END-EXEC.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '****-SITUAÇĂO       '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSHEADER-HRSITU     '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSHEADER-HRSITU         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE CON-PSHEADER               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
      * SE FICHEIRO AGUARDA ANULACAO / ANULADO / CANCELADO
                 IF VIAL0001-MODIFICACAO OR VIAL0001-ANULACAO
                    IF PSHEADER-HRSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-FIC-AGUARDA-AN OR
                       PSHEADER-HRSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-FIC-CANCELADO  OR
                       PSHEADER-HRSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-FIC-ANULADO

                       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                             TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                             TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                       MOVE PSCK0001-FICH-CAN TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
      * SE FICHEIRO PROCESSADO
                 IF VIAL0001-MODIFICACAO
                   IF PSHEADER-HRSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-FIC-ERRADO   OR
                      PSHEADER-HRSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-FIC-PROCESSADO
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '****-VEIO-AO-ERRO   '  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSHEADER-HRSITU     '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSHEADER-HRSITU         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF

                      SET  VIAL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                             TO TRUE
                      MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                             TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                      MOVE PSCK0001-FICH-PROC
                                             TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                   END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 SET  VIAL0002-ABEND-DB2   TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2059-VALIDA-FICHEIRO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNCLI '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNCLI        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORDINT '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORDINT        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNFIC '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNFIC        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'PSCV1820-ORNREG '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (4)
              MOVE  PSCV1820-ORNREG        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNCLI            TO PSDETALHE-DTNCLI.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORDINT            TO AQCW0005-DTX10.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98              TO PSDETALHE-DTDINT.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNFIC            TO PSDETALHE-DTNFIC.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNREG            TO PSDETALHE-DTNREG.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT   DTNCLI
                     , DTDINT
                     , DTNFIC
                     , DTNREG
                     , DTREF
                     , DTTREG
                     , DTTOPE
                     , DTSITC
                     , DTSITR
                     , DTCBAN
                     , DTCBAL
                     , DTCNTA
                     , DTCDIG
                     , DTMONT
                     , DTNOME
                     , DTREFTR
                     , DTDVAL
                     , DTNTRY
                     , DTNOCB
                     , DTSITU
                     , DTMAIL
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEEST
                     , DTNOMEB
                     , DTDDEB
                 INTO  :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTDINT
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNFIC
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNREG
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTREF
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTTREG
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTTOPE
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTSITC
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTSITR
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTCBAN
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTCBAL
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTCNTA
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTCDIG
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTMONT
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNOME
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTREFTR
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTDVAL
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNTRY
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNOCB
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTSITU
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTMAIL
                     , :PSDETALHE-CUSERID
                     , :PSDETALHE-HTIMEEST
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB
                     , :PSDETALHE-DTDDEB
                 FROM PSDETALHE2
                 WHERE   DTNCLI = :PSDETALHE-DTNCLI
                     AND DTDINT = :PSDETALHE-DTDINT
                     AND DTNFIC = :PSDETALHE-DTNFIC
                     AND DTNREG = :PSDETALHE-DTNREG
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-PSDETALH               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNCLI-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTDINT-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNFIC-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNREG-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNREG-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNREG-MSG
                 ELSE
      *
      * SE REGISTO ANULADO / CANCELADO
                    IF (VIAL0001-MODIFICACAO OR
                        VIAL0001-ANULACAO  ) AND
                       (PSDETALHE-DTSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-REG-CANCELADO
                    OR  PSDETALHE-DTSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-REG-ANULADO )

                       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                       MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-REGPROC
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                    END-IF
      * SE REGISTO PROCESSADO
                    IF VIAL0001-MODIFICACAO AND
                      (PSDETALHE-DTSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-REG-ENVIADO-TEI
                    OR PSDETALHE-DTSITU EQUAL PSCK0002-REG-PROCESSADO)

                       MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                       MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-REGPROC
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                    END-IF
      *
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNCLI  TO PSCV1821-ORNCLI
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTDINT  TO AQCW0005-DT98

                    PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                       THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT

                    MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10    TO PSCV1821-ORDINT
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNFIC  TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNREG  TO PSCV1821-ORNREG
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTREF   TO PSCV1821-ORREF
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTTREG  TO PSCV1821-ORTREG
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTTOPE  TO PSCV1821-ORTOPE
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTSITC  TO PSCV1821-ORSITC
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTSITR  TO PSCV1821-ORSITR
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAN  TO PSCV1821-ORCBAN
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCBAL  TO PSCV1821-ORCBAL
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCNTA  TO PSCV1821-ORCNTA
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTCDIG  TO PSCV1821-ORCDIG
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTMONT  TO PSCV1821-ORMONT
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOME  TO PSCV1821-ORNOME
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTREFTR TO PSCV1821-ORREFTR
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTDVAL  TO AQCW0005-DT98

                    PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                       THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT

                    MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10    TO PSCV1821-ORDVAL
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNTRY  TO PSCV1821-ORNTRY
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOCB  TO PSCV1821-ORNOCB
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTMAIL  TO PSCV1821-ORMAIL
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTNOMEB TO PSCV1821-ORNOMEB
                    MOVE PSDETALHE-DTDDEB  TO PSCV1821-ORDDEB

                    IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
                        CONTINUE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTDINT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNFIC-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNREG-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-DTNREG-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV1821-ORNREG-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
              THRU 4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.
       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0380-VERSAO
           MOVE CON-PRG-NAME               TO SXCL0380-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-NOME-CLI      TO SXCL0380-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0380-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0380-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0380-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0380-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0380-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0380-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG         TO SXCL0380-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL         TO SXCL0380-VNCR.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO SXCL0380-CLBAL.
           MOVE PSCV1821-ORCNTA            TO WS-CNTA.
           MOVE WS-CNTA-NCLI               TO SXCL0380-CLNCLI.

           CALL SXCL0380-ROTINA         USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                              SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE SXCL0380-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE SXCL0380-DWT OF SXCL0380-WT OF SXCL0380-DATA(1)
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNOMEBM
           END-IF.
      *
       2299-OBTEM-NOME-BENEF-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0380-VERSAO
           MOVE CON-PRG-NAME               TO SXCL0380-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-NOME-CLI      TO SXCL0380-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0380-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0380-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0380-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0380-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0380-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0380-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG         TO SXCL0380-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL         TO SXCL0380-VNCR.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO SXCL0380-CLBAL.
           MOVE PSCV1820-ORNCLI            TO SXCL0380-CLNCLI.

           CALL SXCL0380-ROTINA         USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                              SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE SXCL0380-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE SXCL0380-DWT OF SXCL0380-WT OF SXCL0380-DATA(1)
                                           TO PSCV1821-ORNMCLI
           END-IF.
      *
       4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE PSCV1821-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV1821-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV1821-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
      *    CONVERSAO DE DATAS
           COPY AQCP0005.
      *    TRATAMENTO DE ERROS
           COPY AQCP0009.
      *    TRATAMENTO DE DEBUG
           COPY VIAP0016.
